## Module Visibility

Default to the most restrictive visibility. Increase only when required.

| Visibility      | Use when                                     |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Private (none)  | Internal implementation details              |
| `pub(crate)`    | Used within the crate but not public API     |
| `pub(super)`    | Used by the parent module only               |
| `pub`           | Stable public API, documented with `///`     |

```rust
mod internal {
    pub(crate) fn helper() { /* ... */ }
}

pub mod api {
    /// Public-facing function — part of the stable API.
    pub fn process(input: &str) -> Result<Output, Error> {
        // ...
    }
}
```

