## Feature Flags

Use Cargo features for optional functionality. Keep the default feature set
minimal.

```toml
# Cargo.toml
[features]
default = []
tls = ["dep:rustls", "dep:tokio-rustls"]
vault = ["dep:vaultrs"]
metrics = ["dep:metrics", "dep:metrics-exporter-prometheus"]
```

```rust
// Conditionally compile behind a feature flag
#[cfg(feature = "vault")]
pub mod vault_client {
    // ...
}
```

**Rules:**
- Feature names are lowercase kebab-case
- Never put security-critical functionality behind an optional feature
- Document each feature in `Cargo.toml` with a comment

