## Project Structure (Single-Crate)

For simpler projects, organise by layer within a single crate.

```
src/
├── main.rs             # Entry point — wiring only, no business logic
├── lib.rs              # Public API re-exports
├── config.rs           # Configuration loading and validation
├── error.rs            # Shared error types
├── domain/             # Domain types and traits
│   ├── mod.rs
│   ├── user.rs
│   └── event.rs
├── service/            # Business logic
│   ├── mod.rs
│   └── user_service.rs
├── repository/         # Data access
│   ├── mod.rs
│   └── user_repository.rs
└── api/                # HTTP layer (handlers, middleware, router)
    ├── mod.rs
    ├── router.rs
    ├── handlers/
    └── middleware/
```

